://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999998863, \"rank\": 7.95616510076397e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mankato Department\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"Public Safety\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 240}, {\"ngram\": \"Cop\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"a Roof\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 259}, {\"ngram\": \"the Dunkin Donuts\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 280}, {\"ngram\": \"Madison Avenue\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 298}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event went from 6 am to 11 am Friday.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The event\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 355}, {\"ngram\": \"6 am\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deputies were handing out different vouchers for different donation amounts.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Deputies\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"different vouchers\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"different donation amounts\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Special Olympics reached out to us I think it was probably three years ago and asked if we wanted to be involved.\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Special Olympics\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 484}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And of course we very quickly jumped on board and became part of the organization,\\\" said Deputy Jase Guetter with the Blue Earth County Sheriff's Office.\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blue_Earth_River\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.280893724807482e-17